title: Anatoliy Matkevych
text:
Anatoliy Matkevych (), (born 17 June 1977) is a <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="FC%20Nyva%20Ternopil">FC Nyva Ternopil</a>.
Matkevych played for <a href="MFC%20Mykolaiv">MFC Mykolaiv</a> during the 2010–11 <a href="Ukrainian%20First%20League">Ukrainian First League</a> season. Matkevych participated the <a href="2007%20AFC%20Champions%20League">2007 AFC Champions League</a> group stages with Al-Ittihad Aleppo.
